channel.title: [SHOWOFF]Mitsubishi Eclipse 1999 Tuning[SHOWOFF]NO SPOILER EDITION + CONTEST
channel.description:
Alright, after a day of hard working I finished the car, it's the Mitsubishi Eclipse 1999, my favorite car. The car is't so good because there was a polygon limit. I'm pretty proud of myself though. I think this model just won the never exising car modeling contest 4. As you can see in the images below, this car was modeled in 3DS Max 2010. Since I had many negative comments about the spoiler of the previous model I made this model that doesn't include a gigantic spoiler.
[size=14pt][b]I got good news for you guys, I am willing to model 1 car for one of you. All you need to do is get me some blueprints of the car you want, top, front and back. Also try to give me the colors and etc. for the car. I will make the car RS2 client capable. But, there will be probably more than 1 user that wants me to model him a car. That's why I'm going to organize a little contest, basicly you have to model a car [b]IN METASEQUOIA[/b] and post a picture here, just give your best shot. I will pick out the best one and model the car he requested for him, I will give the winning user the model and if he allows me to release it, I will. Anyhow, to get blueprints, just go to this awesome website: http://www.the-blueprints.com/blueprints/cars/ and search for your favorite car, and post the blueprints of that car in the comment section below. Good luck. THE WINNER WILL BE ANNOUNCED WHEN I FEEL LIKE IT[/b][/size]
